<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跳到云上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得帮这个王国一段时间了。” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后找到八戒，回到师父身边。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空到达真实储蓄银行的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看到几个穿着蓝色制服的人，还看到了史密斯侦探。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“又见面了，侦探。” 悟空落在他旁边说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是来帮忙的，谁在抢银行，是妖怪吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探翻了个白眼：“很有意思，悟空。强盗不是妖怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空皱了皱眉：“我没开玩笑。算了……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿出金箍棒，“我进去除掉他们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65543</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探大吃一惊：“你说什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65543</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我说去除掉强盗。” 悟空挥着金箍棒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会把他们全部消灭，这样他们就不能再做坏事了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不行，悟空！” 史密斯侦探举起双手，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们只需要逮捕他们，不能伤害他们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对。” 悟空叹了一口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“每个人都在对我说，不能伤害任何人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100411</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>别担心，我一定会好好儿做的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空收起金箍棒，走进银行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个人正在把一堆绿色的小纸片装进袋子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个人看到悟空，大笑起来：“厄尔，看那只猴子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>厄尔笑了：“我也看见了，德怀特！这只猴子长得真好笑！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他从哪儿来的？” 德怀特问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空拍了拍下巴：“我来自于花果山的一块石头。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133278</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“猴子说话了！” 厄尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我会说话。” 悟空笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是来告诉你们，你们被逮捕了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>厄尔和德怀特沉默了一会儿，然后哈哈大笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空也假笑了几声，然后突然开始变大，眼睛也变红了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 两个男人尖叫着跑出银行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不许动！” 一个警察大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>厄尔和德怀特没管警察，迅速开车跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咣！悟空从银行的窗户跳下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看见强盗们的车在拐角处消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空想到一个主意。他迅速念了句咒语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>光芒闪烁！悟空变成了一辆汽车！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呜！悟空的轮胎转动，空中烟雾弥漫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他追着强盗向前冲去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空开心地笑了：“真有趣！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个玩儿杂耍的人真厉害！” 罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219277</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和地主在一个漂亮的房间里吃饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223543</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个人在演奏，一个人在玩儿杂耍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223543</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你有什么超能力？” 地主问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227683</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西耸了耸肩：“我会飞，还能发出激光。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太棒了！” 地主说，“我马上就回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他站起来去了厨房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241476</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得回家了。” 罗西有些着急。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西在这里过得很开心，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 但是她也有些担心：“希望那只猴子不会把美罗城破坏得太严重。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255223</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，她的超级听力听到了远处的一些声音，罗西仔细听着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不。” 她心想，“有人在哭！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>